TextBody:
Hello Jess, 

Sorry for the long reply. Could you please run the following command in cmd as an admin on the server where Netwrix Enterprise Auditor is installed:

Setspn â€“S HTTP/[FQDN] [domain][servername]$ 

Example from my enviroment:
Setspn â€“S HTTP/FILE.IKUD.LOCAL IKUDFILE$

And restart the following service after:

Netwrix Enterprise Auditor Web Server

Please, try to log in to Published Reports - are you still being asked for credentials for Windows Authentication?

Thank you!

Best Regards,
Ilia Kudashev
Support Engineer EMEA
